+companion iteration is now deterministic via npc_id sort
+recruit flow now validates the NPC exists before joining
+inspector diff now shows party deltas
+timeline rows now expose party size
+
+That moves 9.1 from “good scaffold” to “solid integrated phase.”
+
+Two small cautions before 9.2:
+
+the recruit validation you described checks existence, but not hostile/disallowed recruitment yet; that is fine to defer into 9.2 as a rules-layer upgrade
